ital Facade}}</ref>\n\n==See also==\n*[[Kumho Asiana Group]]\n*[[LED]]\n*[[New media art]]\n*[[Light pollution]]\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Coord missing|South Korea}}\n\n[[Category:Buildings and structures in Seoul]]\n[[Category:Kumho Asiana Group]]\n[[Category:Office buildings completed in 2008]]\n\n{{SouthKorea-struct-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox building\n| name                = Kumho Asiana Main Tower\n| native_name         = \n| native_name_lang    = Korean, English\n| former_names        = \n| alternate_names     = \n| status              = \n| image               = \n| image_alt           =\n| image_size          = \n| caption             = \n| map_type            = \n| map_alt             = \n| map_caption         = \n| altitude            = \n| building_type       = Office Building\n| architectural_style = \n| structural_system   = \n| cost                =  \n| ren_cost            = \n| client              = [[Kumho Asiana Group]]\n| owner               = \n| website             =  <small>[http://www.kumhoasiana.com/kumho_en/ Main Official Website]</small>\n| current_tenants     = \n| landlord            = \n| location            = \n| address             = \n| location_town       = [[Seoul]]\n| location_country    = [[South Korea]]\n| coordinates         = \n| groundbreaking_date = \n| start_date          = \n| completion_date     = 2008\n| opened_date         = \n| inauguration_date   = \n| renovation_date     = \n| demolition_date     = \n| destruction_date    = \n| height              = \n| architectural       = \n| tip                 = \n| antenna_spire       = \n| roof                = \n| top_floor           = \n| observatory         = \n| other_dimensions    = \n| floor_count         = 29 Stories and 8 Basements \n| floor_area          = 60,695 sq. meters\n| seating_type        = \n| seating_capacity    = \n| elevator_count      = \n| main_contractor     = \n| architect           =  \n| architecture_firm   = [[Samoo Architects & E