]], [[Pays de la Loire]], [[France]] (1982)<ref name=\"Wexford Twinning\"/><ref name=\"Wexford-Cou\u00ebron\">{{cite web|title=Coueron call to Wexford businesses|publisher=Wexford People|url=https://www.pressreader.com/ireland/wexford-people/20130205/282260957847577|date=5 February 2013|accessdate=18 April 2020}}</ref>\n:{{flagicon|Italy}}{{flagicon|Emilia-Romagna}} [[Lugo, Emilia-Romagna|Lugo]], [[Emilia-Romagna]], [[Italy]] (2013)<ref name=\"Wexford Twinning\"/>\n\n===County Wicklow===\n*[[County Wicklow]]\n:{{flagicon|China}}{{flagicon|Hainan}} [[Hainan|Hainan Province]], [[China]] (2017)<ref name=\"Wicklow County Council\">{{cite web|title=Town Twinning|publisher=Wicklow County Council|url=https://www.wicklow.ie/Living/Your-Council/Town-Twinning/|date=2020|accessdate=16 April 2020}}</ref>\n:{{flagicon|United States}}{{flagicon|Florida}} [[Seminole County, Florida|Seminole County]], [[Florida]], [[United States]] (1991)<ref name=\"County Wicklow-Seminole County\">{{cite web|title=Junkets: Spouses and children travelled too 'because of length of trips'|publisher=Wicklow People|url= https://www.independent.ie/regionals/wicklowpeople/news/junkets-spouses-and-children-travelled-too-because-of-length-of-trips-29251064.html|date=4 May 2013|accessdate=16 April 2020}}</ref>\n:{{flagicon|Germany}}{{flagicon|Bavaria}} [[W\u00fcrzburg]], [[Bavaria]], [[Germany]] (1999)<ref name=\"Wicklow County Council\"/><ref name=\"Wicklow-W\u00fcrzburg\">{{cite web|title=Two-decade friendship between Wicklow and W\u00fcrzburg renewed|publisher=Bray People|url=https://www.independent.ie/regionals/braypeople/news/two-decade-friendship-between-wicklow-and-wurzburg-renewed-38664180.html|date=9 November 2019|accessdate=16 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n*[[Arklow]]\n:{{flagicon|United Kingdom}}{{flagicon|Wales}} [[Aberystwyth]], [[Wales]], [[United Kingdom]] (2016)<ref name=\"Arklow-Aberystwyth\">{{cite web|title=Town Twinning|publisher=Aberystwyth Council|date=2020|url=https://www.aberystwyth.gov.uk/en/community/town-twinning/|accessdate=16 April 2020}}</ref>\n:{{flagicon|France}}{{flagicon|Centre-Val de Loire}} [[Ch\u00e2teaudun]], [[Centre-Val de Loire]], [[France]] (1983)<ref name=\"Wicklow County Council\"/><ref name=\"Arklow-Ch\u00e2teaudun\">{{cite web|title=Arklow to celebrate 35 years of twinning with Chateaudun|publisher=Wicklow People|date=11 May 2018|url=https://www.independent.ie/regionals/wicklowpeople/news/arklow-to-celebrate-35-years-of-twinning-with-chateaudun-36886800.html|accessdate=16 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n*[[Avoca, County Wicklow|Avoca]]\n:{{flagicon|United Kingdom}}{{flagicon|England}} [[Bromham, Wiltshire|Bromham]], [[England]], [[United Kingdom]] (1997)<ref name=\"Avoca-Bromham\">{{cite web|title=Avoca|publisher=Wicklow People|date=5 May 2011|url=https://www.independent.ie/regionals/wicklowpeople/localnotes/avoca-27861613.html|accessdate=16 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n*[[Bray, County Wicklow|Bray]]\n:{{flagicon|France}}{{flagicon|Nouvelle-Aquitaine}} [[B\u00e8gles]], [[Nouvelle-Aquitaine]], [[France]] (1994)<ref name=\"Wicklow County Council\"/><ref name=\"Bray-B\u00e8gles\">{{cite web|title=Twinned with B\u00e8gles|url=https://www.bray.ie/twinned-begles/|publisher=bray.ie|date=2020|accessdate=16 April 2020}}</ref>\n:{{flagicon|United States}}{{flagicon|California}} [[Dublin, California|Dublin]], [[California]], [[United States]] (1987)<ref name=\"U.S. Embassy\"/><ref name=\"Wicklow County Council\"/><ref name=\"Bray-Dublin 1\">{{cite web|title=Twinned with Dublin, California|url=https://www.bray.ie/twinned-dublin-calfornia/|publisher=bray.ie|date=2020|accessdate=16 April 2020}}</ref><ref name=\"Bray-Dublin 2\">{{cite web|title=Dublin: Why this city's namesake isn't its sister|url=https://www.eastbaytimes.com/2017/04/01/how-we-met-bray-ireland-and-dublin-marking-30-years-of-sisterhood/|publisher=eastbaytimes.com|date=1 April 2017|accessdate=16 April 2020}}</ref>\n:{{flagicon|Germany}}{{flagicon|Bavaria}} [[W\u00fcrzburg]], [[Bavaria]], [[Germany