headford.galway-ireland.ie/|date=2020|accessdate=29 April 2020}}</ref>\n:{{flagicon|United States}}{{flagicon|California}} [[Morgan Hill, California|Morgan Hill]], [[California]], [[United States]]<ref name=\"Headford-Morgan Hill\">{{cite web|title=Welcome to Sister Cities of Morgan Hill, CA|publisher=Morgan Hill Sister Cities|url=http://www.morganhillsistercities.com/|date=2020|accessdate=29 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n*[[Oranmore]] \n:{{flagicon|France}}{{flagicon|Brittany}} [[Clohars-Fouesnant]], [[Brittany]], [[France]] (2012)<ref name=\"Oranmore-Clohars-Fouesnant\">{{cite web|title=Oranmore twins with Breton village|publisher=Galway Advertiser|url=https://www.advertiser.ie/index.php/galway/article/51366/oranmore-twins-with-breton-village|date=19 April 2012|accessdate=29 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n*[[Tuam]]\n:{{flagicon|Germany}}{{flagicon|Bavaria}} [[Straubing]], [[Bavaria]], [[Germany]] (1984)<ref name=\"Tuam-Straubing\">{{cite web|title=About the Twinning|publisher=Tuam-Straubing Twinning|url=http://www.tuam-straubing.ie/|date=2020|accessdate=29 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n===County Leitrim===\n\n===County Mayo===\n\n*[[Ballina, County Mayo|Ballina]]\n:{{Flagicon|United States}}{{Flagicon|Massachusetts}} [[Pittsfield, Massachusetts|Pittsfield]], [[Massachusetts]], United States<ref name=\"US embassy list\"/>\n\n===County Roscommon===\n\n===County Sligo===\n\n*[[Sligo]]\n:{{Flagicon|United States}}{{Flagicon|Florida}} [[Tallahassee, Florida|Tallahassee]], [[Florida]], United States<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://tallahasseeirish.org/?page_id=116|title=The Friends of Sligo Ireland Sponsor Irish Related Events|website=Tallahassee Irish Society|access-date=2018-11-08}}</ref>\n\n==Leinster==\n===County Carlow===\n*[[County Carlow]]\n:{{flagicon|United States}}{{flagicon|Iowa}} [[Davenport, Iowa|Davenport]], [[Iowa]], [[United States]] (2006)<ref name=\"Carlow County Council\">{{cite web|title=Carlow County, Ireland|publisher=Carlow County Council|url=http://www.carlow.ie/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Minutes-Municipal-District-of-Carlow-September-2016.pdf|date=8 September 2016|accessdate=18 April 2020}}</ref><ref name=\"County Carlow-Davenport\">{{cite web|title=Carlow County, Ireland|publisher=Davenport Sister Cities|url=http://davenportsistercities.org/communities/carlow-county-ireland/|date=2020|accessdate=18 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n*[[Carlow]]\n:{{flagicon|France}}{{flagicon|Bourgogne-Franche-Comt\u00e9}} [[Dole, Jura|Dole]], [[Bourgogne-Franche-Comt\u00e9]], [[France]]<ref name=\"Carlow County Council\"/>\n:{{flagicon|United Kingdom}}{{flagicon|England}} [[Northwich]], [[England]], [[United Kingdom]]<ref name=\"Carlow County Council\"/>\n:{{flagicon|United States}}{{flagicon|Arizona}} [[Tempe, Arizona|Tempe]], [[Arizona]], [[United States]] (1998)<ref name=\"U.S. Embassy\">{{cite web|title=Sister Cities|publisher=U.S. Embassy in Ireland|url=https://ie.usembassy.gov/our-relationship/policy-history/sister-cities/|date=2020|accessdate=18 April 2020}}</ref><ref name=\"Carlow County Council\"/><ref name=\"Carlow-Tempe\">{{cite web|title=Tempe Sister Cities|publisher=Our Sister Cities|url=http://www.tempesistercities.org/meet-our-sister-cites/|date=2020|accessdate=18 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n*[[Hacketstown]]\n:{{flagicon|United States}}{{flagicon|New Jersey}} [[Hackettstown, New Jersey]], [[United States]] (1995)<ref name=\"Hacketstown-Hackettstown\">{{cite web|title=Hackettstown, N.J., declares 'sister city' relationship with Hacketstown, Ireland|publisher=Leigh Valley Live|url=http://www.lehighvalleylive.com/warren-county/express-times/index.ssf/2011/03/hackettstown_nj_declares_frien.html|date=15 March 2011|accessdate=18 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n*[[Muine Bheag]]\n:{{flagicon|France}}{{flagicon|Brittany}} [[Pont-P\u00e9an]], [[Brittany]], [[France]] (2000)<ref name=\"Muine Bheag-Pont P\u00e9an\">{{cite web|title=PONT PEAN, May 2000|publisher=Bagenalstown, Ireland - Pont Pean, France|url=http://homepage.eircom.net/~carlow/twin3.html|date=2000|accessdate=18 A